  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to study the effect of dexamethasone combined with ondansetron
      on postoperative nausea and vomiting in patients with patient-controlled analgesia after
      video-assisted thoracoscopic surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
